---
import Page from "../layouts/Page.astro";
import Section from "../components/Section.astro";
---

<Page path={Astro.url.pathname} title="Privacy Policy">
	<Section title="Privacy Policy" id="privacy">
		<h4>Data Collection and Use</h4>
		<p>
			We store hashed IP addresses and hardware IDs (HWIDs) to ensure the security of our service. This includes authentication, preventing abuse, and enforcing bans.
		</p>
		<br>
		<p>
			<strong>Retention:</strong> We retain this data only as long as necessary to fulfill these purposes.
		</p>
		<br>
		<p>
			<strong>User Rights:</strong> You may request access to your data or deletion. Please note:
		</p>
			<ul>
				<li>If you are blacklisted, deletion may not be possible depending on the severity of the situation.</li>
				<li>If you have premium access, requesting deletion will automatically revoke your premium access.</li>
			</ul>
		<p>
			To make a request, contact us on our Discord.
		</p>
		<br>
		<p>
			<p><strong>Legal Basis:</strong> We do not process or share your personal data beyond what is necessary for security purposes. All data handling is based on our <a href="https://gdpr-info.eu/art-6-gdpr/" target="_blank">legitimate interest (Article 6(1)(f) GDPR)</a> in maintaining the safety of our service.</p>
		</p>
	</Section>
</Page>
